## ðŸ’¡ Implementation

Themes use CSS custom properties (variables) to enable instant switching:

```css
[data-theme="pca"] {
  --theme-primary: #2563eb;
  --theme-font-family: Inter;
  --theme-border-radius: 4px;
}

[data-theme="shopsmiles"] {
  --theme-primary: #22c55e;  
  --theme-font-family: Nunito;
  --theme-border-radius: 12px;
}
```

Components reference these variables:
```vue
<button class="bg-[var(--theme-primary)] rounded-[var(--theme-border-radius)]">
  Click Me
</button>
```

